生活嘅期待，呢排好down，夜晚成日諗諗下野就想喊，但已經喊唔出，呢啲其實係咪成長的痛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"0f5edc532588e02dedf2a60dff42b64e9b2c5570","tid":1662343,"uid":221401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a1da24b409ebe120af457abb5884302802939f","tid":1662343,"uid":41161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"依家final year,hea 咗三年都好似唔夠開心咁，完全唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"我都好唔想返工，但又冇得逃避，如果可以讀耐啲大學就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac17a3ee05935d301658b26c8d8b3d76904bda1","tid":1662343,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f5edc532588e02dedf2a60dff42b64e9b2c5570","tid":1662343,"uid":221401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a1da24b409ebe120af457abb5884302802939f","tid":1662343,"uid":41161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"依家final year,hea 咗三年都好似唔夠開心咁，完全唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"我都好唔想返工，但又冇得逃避，如果可以讀耐啲大學就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"如果太大壓力可以defer1年當俾啲空間時間自己先"},{"pid":"9be622a1034e0068ab8f46706adc004321657a8b","tid":1662343,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔會有"},{"pid":"9bfceacb9b42738323299566a81895d5ddc45bef","tid":1662343,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"我都係